[[File:Bronze pickaxe detail.png|left|130px]]
A '''bronze pickaxe''' is a [[pickaxe]] made of [[bronze equipment|bronze]]. It is given to players during the [[Mining]] part of [[Tutorial Island]] when players first start out. It is the lowest-grade pickaxe.

Bronze pickaxes spawn in several locations in Misthalin and Asgarnia, and they can also be bought from various shops.

